<p id="p-rc_c3c52cddf277798e-569" data-path-to-node="14,5,1,0"><span class="citation-68527 citation-68528 citation-68529">Neol</span><span class="citation-68526 citation-68527 citation-68528 citation-68529 citation-end-68529">ithic innovations include:<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="175"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-68526 citation-68527 citation-68528 citation-end-68528"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="176"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-68526 citation-68527 citation-end-68527"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="177"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-68526 citation-end-68526"><sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="178"><!----></sup></span></p>
