<p id="p-rc_c3c52cddf277798e-572" data-path-to-node="14,5,2,0"><span class="citation-68517 citation-68518 citation-end-68518">Each field at Céide was large enough to su<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="186"><!----></sup></span><span class="citation-68517">pport a big {family}</span><span class="citation-68517 citation-end-68517"> .<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="187"><!----></sup></span></p>
