<p id="p-rc_c3c52cddf277798e-573" data-path-to-node="14,5,3,0"><span class="citation-68516 citation-end-68516">The fields were probably used to restrict the grazing of animals – no evidence of structures to house them du<sup class="superscript" data-turn-source-index="188"><!----></sup></span>ring {winter} .</p>
